title: Should we release a limited token to be minted with current $SALMON?
body:
You will only be able to mint this token with existing $SALMON.

This token will be of a bucket, either bronze, silver, or gold, and will be filled with salmon. The bucket will read "World Fishing Championship", and will be an ERC 1155 token acting as a minting pass for use within BearDAO projects.

ERC 1155 tokens are low cost to mint and minting will be done with $SALMON. The three tiers are: Bronze for 100k, Silver for 500k, and Gold for 1M, respectively.

The bronze token will offer free whitelist for one project, silver will offer one free mint for one project, and the gold will be one free mint for all projects launched with BearDAO.

The decision to launch this token will mean that we launch this prior to resetting the game, and requires that we give time to current $SALMON holders to take advantage and mint, if they'd like. If you are in favour of this decision, please be mindful that this will push the game reset time back a bit.
